<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8">
<title>Portfolio Attestation — {{ presenter_brand }}</title>
<style>
@page {
    size: Letter;
    margin: 0.75in;
    @bottom-center {
        content: "Issued by {{ presenter_brand }} on the OsirisCare substrate.  Verify: {{ verify_phone }} or {{ verify_url_short }}.  Valid until {{ valid_until_human }}.";
        font-family: 'Helvetica', 'Arial', sans-serif;
        font-size: 9pt;
        color: #666;
    }
}
body {
    font-family: 'Helvetica', 'Arial', sans-serif;
    color: #222;
    line-height: 1.5;
    font-size: 11pt;
}
.letterhead {
    border-bottom: 2px solid #14A89E;
    padding-bottom: 16px;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
}
.letterhead h1 {
    font-size: 26pt;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #1a365d;
    margin: 0 0 4px 0;
    letter-spacing: -0.5px;
}
.letterhead .partner-name {
    font-size: 18pt;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #2d3748;
    margin: 0 0 6px 0;
}
.letterhead .period {
    font-size: 11pt;
    color: #4a5568;
    margin: 0;
}
.statement {
    margin: 24px 0;
    font-size: 11.5pt;
    line-height: 1.6;
}
.statement p {
    margin: 0 0 14px 0;
}
.metrics {
    margin: 22px 0;
    padding: 16px 18px;
    background: #f0f9ff;
    border-left: 3px solid #0284c7;
    font-size: 11pt;
}
.metrics table {
    width: 100.000%;
    border-collapse: collapse;
}
.metrics td {
    padding: 4px 6px;
    color: #2d3748;
}
.metrics .num {
    text-align: right;
    font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #1a365d;
}
.attestation-block {
    margin-top: 28px;
    padding: 14px 16px;
    background: #f7fafc;
    border-left: 3px solid #14A89E;
    font-size: 10pt;
    color: #4a5568;
}
.attestation-block .label {
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #2d3748;
}
.attestation-block .hash {
    font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
    font-size: 9pt;
    word-break: break-all;
}
.disclaimer {
    margin-top: 22px;
    font-size: 9pt;
    color: #718096;
    line-height: 1.4;
}
.disclaimer p { margin: 0 0 6px 0; }
.cover-paragraph {
    margin-top: 28px;
    padding: 14px 16px;
    background: #f0fff4;
    border-left: 3px solid #38a169;
    font-size: 10pt;
    color: #2d3748;
}
.cover-paragraph .label {
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 6px;
    display: block;
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="letterhead">
    <h1>Portfolio Attestation</h1>
    <p class="partner-name">{{ presenter_brand }}</p>
    <p class="period">For the period {{ period_start_human }} through {{ period_end_human }}</p>
</div>

<div class="statement">
    <p>
        <strong>{{ presenter_brand }}</strong> operates the OsirisCare compliance substrate across <strong>{{ site_count }}</strong> client site{{ 's' if site_count != 1 else '' }}, comprising <strong>{{ appliance_count }}</strong> compliance appliance{{ 's' if appliance_count != 1 else '' }}, <strong>{{ workstation_count }}</strong> monitored workstation{{ 's' if workstation_count != 1 else '' }}, and <strong>{{ control_count }}</strong> continuously monitored technical control{{ 's' if control_count != 1 else '' }} drawn from the published OsirisCare check catalog.
    </p>
    <p>
        Each site's evidence is Ed25519-signed at the appliance edge, hash-chained per site, and anchored via OpenTimestamps to the Bitcoin blockchain. As of {{ chain_head_at_human }}, <strong>{{ ots_anchored_pct_str }}%</strong> of the {{ bundle_count }} evidence bundle{{ 's' if bundle_count != 1 else '' }} captured during this period are anchor-confirmed; the remainder are pending confirmation per the standard OTS schedule.
    </p>
</div>

<div class="metrics">
    <table>
        <tr><td>Client sites monitored</td><td class="num">{{ site_count }}</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Compliance appliances</td><td class="num">{{ appliance_count }}</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Monitored workstations</td><td class="num">{{ workstation_count }}</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Technical controls covered</td><td class="num">{{ control_count }}</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Evidence bundles in period</td><td class="num">{{ bundle_count }}</td></tr>
        <tr><td>OTS anchor coverage</td><td class="num">{{ ots_anchored_pct_str }}%</td></tr>
    </table>
</div>

<div class="cover-paragraph">
    <span class="label">For the recipient (insurance carrier, auditor, prospective client, or counsel):</span>
    This attestation describes technical monitoring coverage performed by {{ presenter_brand }} on the OsirisCare substrate during the stated period. It is audit-supportive aggregate evidence; it contains no protected health information and identifies no individual client. To independently verify this attestation, call {{ verify_phone }} during business hours or visit {{ verify_url_short }}/{{ attestation_hash[:32] }}. Per-site evidence and per-site attestation letters are available to each covered entity through their own client portal.
</div>

<div class="attestation-block">
    <p><span class="label">Issued by:</span> {{ presenter_brand }}{{ presenter_contact_line }}</p>
    <p><span class="label">Substrate:</span> OsirisCare — issuer of Ed25519 signing keys and OpenTimestamps anchors referenced in this attestation</p>
    <p><span class="label">Issuance:</span> {{ issued_at_human }} &nbsp;|&nbsp; <span class="label">Valid until:</span> {{ valid_until_human }} (90 days)</p>
    <p><span class="label">Attestation hash:</span> <span class="hash">{{ attestation_hash }}</span></p>
    <p><span class="label">Chain root:</span> <span class="hash">{{ chain_root_hex }}</span></p>
    <p><span class="label">Verify:</span> {{ verify_phone }} or {{ verify_url_short }}/{{ attestation_hash[:32] }}</p>
</div>

<div class="disclaimer">
    <p>This attestation is audit-supportive technical evidence. It is not a HIPAA §164.528 disclosure accounting and does not constitute a legal opinion. Site-level evidence and per-site attestation letters are available to each covered entity through their client portal. PHI is scrubbed at the appliance before egress.</p>
    <p>Aggregate counts are computed from {{ presenter_brand }}'s active site assignments at issuance time. Counts may shift between issuances as {{ presenter_brand }} adds or completes client engagements; the attestation hash binds to the snapshot at issue. To report a concern about this attestation or the underlying program, contact compliance@osiriscare.com (best-effort acknowledgment within 7 business days; substantive response within 30 days) or the HHS Office for Civil Rights at hhs.gov/ocr/complaints.</p>
</div>

</body>
</html>
